nce/security/infrastructure/ui/docs/test\n   - patternsApplied: comma-separated patterns used (e.g. \"repository pattern, debounce, memoization\")\n\n2. Verify: `npx tsc --noEmit` (fix any type errors)\n\nBegin implementation now."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"786d9178-9299-49ef-a4b8-8ab7c8d6da12","uuid":"a4b8bb19-4d39-4003-93ca-b5c4190ba95f","timestamp":"2026-03-18T12:35:47.941Z","isSynthetic":true}
